5module Koshucode.Baala.Rop.Flat.Message
6  ( module Koshucode.Baala.Rop.Base.Message,
7    checkTerm,

12    dumpTrees,

14    reqBool,
15    reqRel,
16    reqCollection,
17    reqInterp,
18    reqNewTerm,
19    reqUnaryFn,
20    unexpTermName,
21    unmatchShare,
22  ) where
23
24import qualified Koshucode.Baala.Base           as B
25import qualified Koshucode.Baala.Syntax         as S
26import qualified Koshucode.Baala.Data           as D
27import qualified Koshucode.Baala.Core           as C
28import qualified Koshucode.Baala.Data.Message   as Msg
29import Koshucode.Baala.Rop.Base.Message
30
31
32-- ----------------------  Op package
33
34-- | check-term failed
35checkTerm :: String -> [S.TermName] -> D.Head -> B.Ab a
36checkTerm label ns he =
37    Left $ B.abortLines "check-term failed"
38         $ detailTermRel label ns he
39
40-- | Different headings
41diffHead :: [D.Head] -> B.Ab a
42diffHead = Left . B.abortLines "Different headings" . map showHead
43
44-- | Dump content expression
45dumpCox :: (Show c) => c -> B.Ab a
46dumpCox cox = Left $ B.abortLines "Dump content expression"
47                   $ lines $ show cox
48
49-- | Dump relation
50dumpRel :: (D.CRel c, B.MixShortEncode c) => D.Rel c -> B.Ab a
51dumpRel r = Left $ B.abortPage "Dump relation" $ C.relTableLines [] r
52
53-- | Dump token trees
54dumpTrees :: [S.TTree] -> B.Ab a
55dumpTrees trees = Left $ B.abortLines "Dump token trees"
56                   $ lines $ show $ S.ttDoc trees
57
58-- | Duplicate term name
59dupTerm :: (D.GetTermNames t) => t -> B.Ab a
60dupTerm t =
61    Left $ B.abortLines "Duplicate term name"
62         $ msgTerms2 "Duplicate" t' "in the terms" t
63        where t' = B.duplicates $ D.getTermNames t
64
65-- | Odd attribute
66oddAttr :: B.Ab a
67oddAttr = Left $ B.abortBecause "Odd attribute"
68
69-- | Require Boolean
70reqBool :: B.Ab a
71reqBool = Left $ B.abortBecause "Require Boolean"
72
73-- | Require relation
74reqRel :: B.Ab a
75reqRel = Left $ B.abortBecause "Require relation"
76
77-- | Require collection type
78reqCollection :: B.Ab a
79reqCollection = Left $ B.abortBecause "Require collection type"
80
81-- | Require data interpretation
82reqInterp :: B.Ab a
83reqInterp = Left $ B.abortBecause "Require data interpretation"
84
85-- | Require new term names
86reqNewTerm :: (D.GetTermNames t1, D.GetTermNames t2) => t1 -> t2 -> B.Ab a
87reqNewTerm t1 t2 =
88    Left $ B.abortLines "Require new term names"
89         $ Msg.msgTerms2 "Present" t1 "in the terms" t2
90
91-- | Require unary function
92reqUnaryFn :: B.Ab a
93reqUnaryFn = Left $ B.abortBecause "Require unary function"
94
95-- | Unexpected term names
96unexpTermName :: B.Ab a
97unexpTermName = Left $ B.abortBecause "Unexpected term names"
98
99showHead :: D.Head -> String
100showHead = unwords . D.getTermNames
101
102-- | Unmatch shared terms.
103unmatchShare :: [S.TermName] -> [S.TermName] -> B.Ab a
104unmatchShare e a =
105    Left $ B.abortLines "Unmatch shared terms"
106         $ expectActual (ts e) (ts a)
107    where ts xs = unwords $ S.showTermName <$> xs
108
